1. GNOME Terminal
2. Vim Bindings
3. Vim Plugins

1. GNOME Terminal:

(Change default terminal at)
sudo update-alternatives --config x-terminal-emulator

(Tab creation/deletion)
Ctrl+n 'new tab'
ctrl+k 'kill tab'

(Navigation)
shift+j 'move to previous tab'
shift+k 'move to next tab'
shift+h 'move tab to the left'
shift+l 'move tab to teh right'
shift+/ 'search'
shift+n 'find next'

2. Vim Bindings:

(Tool)
fj 'auto indent the entire file'

(Navigation)
ctrl+(hjkl) to 'switch around the Vims inside a same terminal'

3. Vim Plugins:

(Languages)
Typescript: https://github.com/leafgarland/typescript-vim
